e internal\" href=\"#creating-rhostmush-with-a-provided-db\">1.6. Creating RHostMUSH with a Provided DB</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#important-before-you-actually-start-building\">1.6.1. Important before you actually start building</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#using-the-prebuilt-flatfile\">1.6.2. Using the prebuilt flatfile</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#to-load-a-prebuilt-flatfile\">1.6.2.1. To load a prebuilt flatfile</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#almost-backwards-instructions-for-compiling-and-starting-a-mush\">1.7. Almost Backwards Instructions for Compiling and Starting a MUSH</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#basic-instructions-for-starting-a-new-rhostmush\">1.8. Basic Instructions for starting a new RhostMUSH</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#manual-configuration-of-source-code\">1.8.1. Manual configuration of source code</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#loading-a-database-for-your-mush\">1.8.2. Loading a database for your MUSH</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#option-only-perform-these-steps-if-using-a-provided-database\">1.8.2.1. Option: Only perform these steps if using a provided database</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#configure-the-netrhost-conf-file-for-your-mush\">1.8.2.1.1. Configure the netrhost.conf file for your MUSH</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#start-a-mush-and-logging-on-for-the-first-time\">1.9. Start a  MUSH and logging on for the first time</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#option-things-to-do-once-you-have-connected-if-you-did-not-use-a-provided-database\">1.9.1. Option: Things to do once you have connected if you did NOT use a provided database</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#customtize-the-textfiles-for-your-game\">1.10. Customtize the textfiles for your game</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#three-options-for-starting-a-mush\">1.11. Three Options for Starting a MUSH</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#option-1-creating-a-new-game-with-a-blank-database\">1.11.1. Option 1: Creating a new game with a blank database</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#options-2-creating-a-new-game-with-ambrosia-s-default-database\">1.11.2. Options 2: Creating a new game with Ambrosia\u2019s default database</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#option-3-creating-a-new-game-with-the-generic-default-database\">1.11.3. Option 3: Creating a new game with the generic default database</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#starting-your-mush\">1.12. Starting your MUSH</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": true, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "install", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12", "karma_sphinx_theme_version": "0.0.8"}